{{!--
  Generic Cyberpunk "save-prompt" chat card. Replaces the inline-HTML content blocks that
  the combat module used to build by hand (one template instead of ~18 copies).

  Params (both pre-localized; light inline <b> emphasis in the i18n strings is intentional):
    title  heading text. When present it renders as an <h3>, and `body` (if any) goes in a
           <div class="save-info"> beneath it (the structured card look).
    body   the card text. When there is no `title`, body renders flat inside the prompt div
           (for short one-line reminders, e.g. "X is still held by Y").
--}}
<div class="cyberpunk save-prompt">
{{#if title}}
  <h3>{{{title}}}</h3>
  {{#if body}}<div class="save-info">{{{body}}}</div>{{/if}}
{{else}}
  {{{body}}}
{{/if}}
</div>
